MODULE
     mod_dir - Basic directory handling.

DESCRIPTION
     This module generates an  HTML  directory  listing  (Apache-
     style)  if  a client sends a request for a directory instead
     of a file. This module is not configurable and it  needs  to
     be  removed  from  the Modules config directive if directory
     listings is unwanted.


